data.description:
WALK- OUT * LOFT AREA * OPEN CONCEPT * 3-CAR GARAGE * FINISHED BASEMENT * GRANITE * STAINLESS APPLIANCES * LARGE ISLAND * STUCCO * MAPLE CABINETS 

This home has it all and the open and inviting floor plan will dazzle!  The elegant foyer offers a nice welcome and leads you into the great room boasting gorgeous windows,earthy laminate wood flooring, fireplace and vaulted ceilings.  The kitchen is a gourmet's delight with coveted maple cabinetry in a gorgeous ashy stain, granite slab surfaces and an expansive island ideal for work space and serving.  Entertaining will be a breeze in this home as there is tons of room on the main level but the basement living area adds even more space for those fun family/friend gatherings.  Meander upstairs and you will find the added bonus of a loft area which is ideal for a kiddo's study space or office area.  The master is a nice retreat with a private bathroom boasting a large walk-in tiled shower.  The walk-in closet is very large with tons of options.  The other two guest bedrooms can be found on this level and the convenience of the upper level laundry will be appreciated by all.
